Kimotion Hackathon

what?

Kimotion is a framework for building interactive art exhibits. With a pinch of JavaScript, Kinect, WebGL, and WebSockets you can create awesome interactive visualizations.

Why?

Kimotion began as an interactive digital art exhibit at SPARKcon called Digital Motion. It morphed from an exhibit into a tool for building exhibits.










Why do you care?

Make a Kimotion

Today, we're making mods for Kimotion. Anything you create will be featured at SPARKcon.
